      "file_path": "kubernetes/common/common/templates/_service.tpl",
      "patchset_number": 28,
      "line": 122,
      "message": "yup it looks fine so now the trick that you can do to avoid assigning this special NONE value would be:\ndefine makeSuffix\n  if hasKey .Values.service.headless \"suffix\"\n    .Values.service.headless.suffix\n  else\n     \"headless\"\n\nthis way you can do in your values files:\nsuffix: \"\"\nand it will drop the headless suffix from your service name:)",
